entry.title: Our polling this month showed that 73% of young people (aged 18-29) support the Voice to Parliament. Young people have a very important role to play in talking to their parents and grandparents about why they support the Yes vote & their hopes for the fut
entry.content: Our polling this month showed that 73% of young people (aged 18-29) support the Voice to Parliament. Young people have a very important role to play in talking to their parents and grandparents about why they support the Yes vote & their hopes for the future of our nation.
